				<td colspan="2"><span>Ok, I know that every little bit of skill helps, but how much?
<br />

<br />
Has anyone figured out how much each point of Defense effects how often you get hit?  Any log parses?  I admit that in leveling so fast as you can these days, my Def is lacking.  What I am wondering is, is it worth it to take some time off and work on it, or should I just not worry and go level up?
<br />

<br />
Level 57 now and only 187 def here.  Parry is going up real nicely though!
<br />

<br />
Tenosh on Prexus.
<br />

<br />
<i>edit: changed my def skill to what it really is, now that it just went up a point tonight!</i></span></td>
