				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">Has anyone figured out how much each point of Defense effects how often you get hit? Any log parses?</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
There are far too many variables to give any sort of definative or accurate answer to that question.
<br />

<br />
I wouldnt be too overly concerned about your defensive skill. 187 is not great, but it's not terrible. I recall being stuck around 190 until I hit level 65. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
If you can find a spot with some low blue or light blue mobs that you can melee solo, you can work up your skill fairly easily.
<br />

<br />
Conversely, what I did is just get natural skillups via getting whacked on pulls before the tank got aggro. 
<br />

<br />
A guildmate of mine liked to get big swarms and fire off Kizumis (whenever it refreshed) and run into the middle of his swarm. He claimed he got most of his post 175 defensive skillups using that method.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
