				<td colspan="2"><span>Kazumi's defintely works, although the refresh timer is a drag.
<br />

<br />
As the last poster suggested, get into pulling and your defense will steadily increase. LDoN pulling got mine maxed in a matter of weeks.
<br />

<br />
That said, I believe maxed defense might help you a fraction in one-on-one encounters, but in a group or raid you're still going to die as fast as anyone else if the unpleasant stuff hits the fan. So not a huge thing to worry about.
<br />
