				<td colspan="2"><span>Actually, Defense skill ALSO translates directly to Armor Class -- and while I don't have the exact numbers at different levels, you can play around with a Magelo profile and watch the changes in your AC as you raise or lower the defense skill.
<br />

<br />
I had def maxed before LDON came out.  I got from about 180 to 252 duoing with a druid at Ssra Temple in the Grey root-dotting.  Whenever we got trained by people running fully visible to the temple, I would charm mobs and we'd fight our way through the mess and that's how I got most of my skill ups.</span></td>
