				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: The Value of a skill<a name="19028"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 4 04 11:34 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>One of the simplest way to raise defense is to have multiple mobs hitting you at the same time.  
<br />

<br />
In an ideal case grab a cleric and a druid and bring some shaman potions (DS).
<br />

<br />
Have the druid cast his DS on you and have the cleric pull with mark of the  righteous or mark of karn.  Get 6-10 mobs on you. (You just need to hit them once to aggro and they will grind themselves to dust on your 60+ pt DS if you sing one too).  
<br />

<br />
You will see that defense is maxed in a very very short time.</span></td>
